/**
*<div id="function.pg-get-pid" class="refentry">    <div class="refnamediv">     <h1 class="refname">pg_get_pid</h1>     <p class="verinfo">(PHP 4 &gt;= 4.3.0, PHP 5, PHP 7)</p><p class="refpurpose"><span class="refname">pg_get_pid</span> &mdash; <span class="dc-title">Ping 数据库连接</span></p>     </div>    <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 unknown-unknown-seealsq" id="refsect1-function.pg-get-pid-unknown-unknown-seealsq">     <h3 class="title">说明</h3>      <div class="methodsynopsis dc-description" style="border:1px gray;padding-left:5px;background:#232525">       <span class="type" style="color:#EAB766">int</span> <span class="methodname" style="color:#CC7832"><strong>pg_get_pid</strong></span>        ( <span class="methodparam"><span class="type" style="color:#EAB766">resource</span> <span class="parameter" style="color:#2EACF9">$connection</span></span>       )</div>      <p class="para rdfs-comment">      <span class="function"><strong style="color:#CC7832">pg_get_pid()</strong></span> 取得后端（数据库服务器进程）的      PID。PID 用来检查其它进程是否发送了      <em>NOTIFY</em> 消息。     </p>     <p class="para">      <div class="example" id="example-2495">       <p><strong>Example #1 PostgreSQL 后端 PID</strong></p>       <div class="example-contents"> <div class="phpcode" style="border-color:gray;background:#232525"><span><span style="color: #000000"> <span style="color: #9876AA">&lt;?php&nbsp;<br />$conn&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #007700">=&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #9876AA">pg_pconnect</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"dbname=publisher"</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br />if&nbsp;(!</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$conn</span><span style="color: #007700">)&nbsp;{<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;echo&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"An&nbsp;error&nbsp;occured.\n"</span><span style="color: #007700">;<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;exit;<br />}<br /><br /></span><span style="color: #FF8000">//&nbsp;Backend&nbsp;process&nbsp;PID.&nbsp;Use&nbsp;PID&nbsp;with&nbsp;pg_get_notify()<br /></span><span style="color: #9876AA">$pid&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #007700">=&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #9876AA">pg_get_pid</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$conn</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br /></span><span style="color: #9876AA">?&gt;</span> </span> </span></div>       </div>       </div>     </p>     <p class="para">      参见 <span class="function">{@link pg_get_notify()}</span>。     </p>    </div>    <div class="up"><a href="http://php.net/manual/zh/ref.pgsql.php">PostgreSQL 函数</a></div></div>
