/**
*<div id="function.pg-untrace" class="refentry">    <div class="refnamediv">     <h1 class="refname">pg_untrace</h1>     <p class="verinfo">(PHP 4 &gt;= 4.0.1, PHP 5, PHP 7)</p><p class="refpurpose"><span class="refname">pg_untrace</span> &mdash; <span class="dc-title">关闭 PostgreSQL 连接的追踪功能</span></p>     </div>    <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 unknown-unknown-unknown-examplev" id="refsect1-function.pg-untrace-unknown-unknown-unknown-examplev">     <h3 class="title">说明</h3>      <div class="methodsynopsis dc-description" style="border:1px gray;padding-left:5px;background:#232525">       <span class="type" style="color:#EAB766">bool</span> <span class="methodname" style="color:#CC7832"><strong>pg_untrace</strong></span>        ([ <span class="methodparam"><span class="type" style="color:#EAB766">resource</span> <span class="parameter" style="color:#2EACF9">$connection</span></span>      ] )</div>      <p class="para rdfs-comment">      停止由 <span class="function">{@link pg_trace()}</span> 启动的追踪功能。<span class="parameter" style="color:#2EACF9">connection</span> 指定了被追踪的连接号，默认为上一个打开的连接。     </p>     <p class="para">      本函数总是返回 <strong><span>TRUE</span></strong>。     </p>     <p class="para">      参见 <span class="function">{@link pg_trace()}</span>。     </p>    </div>    <div class="up"><a href="http://php.net/manual/zh/ref.pgsql.php">PostgreSQL 函数</a></div></div>
