ss="para">        PostgreSQL database connection resource.  When         <span class="parameter" style="color:#2EACF9">connection</span> is not present, the default connection         is used. The default connection is the last connection made by         <span class="function">{@link pg_connect()}</span> or <span class="function">{@link pg_pconnect()}</span>.       </p>      </dd>                 <dt> <span class="parameter" style="color:#2EACF9">oid</span></dt>       <dd>        <p class="para">        The <var class="varname"><var class="varname">OID</var></var> of the large object in the database.       </p>      </dd>          </dl>    </span>  </div>    <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 returnvalues" id="refsect1-function.pg-lo-unlink-returnvalues">   <h3 class="title">返回值</h3>   <p class="para">    成功时返回 <strong><span>TRUE</span></strong>， 或者在失败时返回 <strong><span>FALSE</span></strong>。   </p>  </div>     <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 examples" id="refsect1-function.pg-lo-unlink-examples">   <h3 class="title">范例</h3>   <span>    <div class="example" id="example-2501">     <p><strong>Example #1 <span class="function"><strong style="color:#CC7832">pg_lo_unlink()</strong></span> example</strong></p>     <div class="example-contents"> <div class="phpcode" style="border-color:gray;background:#232525"><span><span style="color: #000000"> <span style="color: #9876AA">&lt;?php<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #FF8000">//&nbsp;OID&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;large&nbsp;object&nbsp;to&nbsp;delete<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$doc_oid&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #007700">=&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #9876AA">189762345</span><span style="color: #007700">;<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$database&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #007700">=&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #9876AA">pg_connect</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"dbname=jacarta"</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #9876AA">pg_query</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$database</span><span style="color: #007700">,&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"begin"</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #9876AA">pg_lo_unlink</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$database</span><span style="color: #007700">,&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$doc_oid</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #9876AA">pg_query</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$database</span><span style="color: #007700">,&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"commit"</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br /></span><span style="color: #9876AA">?&gt;</span> </span> </span></div>     </div>     </div>    </span>  </div>     <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 seealso" id="refsect1-function.pg-lo-unlink-seealso">   <h3 class="title">参见</h3>   <span>    <ul class="simplelist">     <li class="member"><span class="function">{@link pg_lo_create()} - 新建一个大型对象</span></li>     <li class="member"><span class="function">{@link pg_lo_import()} - 将文件导入为大型对象</span></li>    </ul>   </span>  </div>    <div class="up"><a href="http://php.net/manual/zh/ref.pgsql.php">PostgreSQL 函数</a></div></div>
