gray solid"><p><strong class="note" style="border:1px gray solid">Note</strong>:     <p class="para">     本函数以前的名字为 <span class="function"><strong style="color:#CC7832">pg_loimport()</strong></span>。    </p>   </p></blockquote>    </div>    <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 parameters" id="refsect1-function.pg-lo-import-parameters">   <h3 class="title">参数</h3>   <span>    <dl>            <dt> <span class="parameter" style="color:#2EACF9">connection</span></dt>       <dd>        <p class="para">        PostgreSQL database connection resource.  When         <span class="parameter" style="color:#2EACF9">connection</span> is not present, the default connection         is used. The default connection is the last connection made by         <span class="function">{@link pg_connect()}</span> or <span class="function">{@link pg_pconnect()}</span>.       </p>      </dd>                 <dt> <span class="parameter" style="color:#2EACF9">pathname</span></dt>       <dd>        <p class="para">        变量指明了要导入为大型对象的文件名。       </p>      </dd>                 <dt> <span class="parameter" style="color:#2EACF9">object_id</span></dt>       <dd>        <p class="para">        If an <span class="parameter" style="color:#2EACF9">object_id</span> is given the function        will try to create a large object with this id, else a free        object id is assigned by the server. The parameter        was added in PHP 5.3 and relies on functionality that first        appeared in PostgreSQL 8.1.       </p>      </dd>          </dl>    </span>  </div>    <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 returnvalues" id="refsect1-function.pg-lo-import-returnvalues">   <h3 class="title">返回值</h3>   <p class="para">    导入成功则返回新建的大型对象的 <var class="varname"><var class="varname">OID</var></var>，如果出错则返回 <strong><span>FALSE</span></strong>。   </p>  </div>    <br></br><div 